# Task management rules

## Overview
There are 3 sections:
- Section 1 includes:
  High Priority Tasks
  Medium Priority Tasks
  Low Priority Tasks
- Section 2 includes:
  Completed Tasks
  In Progress Tasks

## Requirement
- Just do 1 task at the time
- Which task is in implemented then mark that task with "current doing" then copy that task and move to "In Progress Tasks" section
- After done this task then mark task as completed by changing `[ ]` to `[x]`